legend right
  | Color | Layer |
  |<#80E0D0> Teal | Engine Context + Resolution + Measures (shared) |
  |<#FFCC66> Gold | Domain Config Loading |
  |<#FF9933> Orange | Build Path (Spark) |
  |<#3399FF> Blue | Query Path (DuckDB / Spark) |
